            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Nilii </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> vigiliis adque consilio domi <supplied reason="lost">fo</supplied>risque pr<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>e<lb break="no" n="2"/>stanti integritate praecipuo iustitia <lb n="3"/>et iud<supplied reason="lost">ic</supplied>i<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>rum mo<supplied reason="lost">d</supplied>eratione perpenso <lb n="4"/>instauratori moenium publicorum <lb n="5"/>ordinis civi<supplied reason="lost">umq</supplied>u<supplied reason="lost">e omnium</supplied> salut<supplied reason="lost">is pr</supplied>o<lb break="no" n="6"/>vide<supplied reason="lost">ntissimo</supplied> custodi <supplied reason="lost">veritatis honesta</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>tis et fi<supplied reason="lost">dei a</supplied>micissimo <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Archontio Nilo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> com<supplied reason="lost">iti et p</supplied>raes<supplied reason="lost">idi</supplied> <lb n="9"/>provi<supplied reason="lost">nciae <expan><abbr>Trip</abbr><ex>olitanae</ex></expan> patrono optimo ob infinita</supplied> <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">eius beneficia quibus vel separat</supplied>im vel <lb n="11"/>cum omn<supplied reason="lost">i pr</supplied>ovincia su<supplied reason="lost">ble</supplied>va<supplied reason="lost">ti ac</supplied> recrae<lb break="no" n="12"/>ati <note>sic</note> Lepcimagnenses gratula<supplied reason="lost">mur un</supplied>o c<supplied reason="lost">on</supplied><lb break="no" n="13"/>sensu statuam decreverunt e<supplied reason="lost">am</supplied>q<supplied reason="lost">ue propter</supplied> <lb n="14"/>praecipuum eius meritum coloniae <supplied reason="lost">ornatui</supplied> <lb n="15"/>censuerunt esse iungendam
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): AE 1948: Z. 2-14: geringfügige Leseabweichungen; Z. 15-16: coloniae / censuerunt. Interpunktion: Palmette und kleiner Kranz.</p>
            </div>
